posting_body: ['CHARMING 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom - GROUND FLOOR W/PATIO - $1,325 per month', '11054 4th Ave SW , Burien, WA 98146', 'FEATURES', 'Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Located on Floor #:', '1', 'Floors in Bldg:', '3', 'Square Footage:', '690', 'Parking Spaces:', '1', 'Pets Allowed:', 'Case By Case', 'DESCRIPTION', 'We currently have a bottom floor 1 bedroom, 1 bath apartment home with a small yard.', 'PICTURES TO FOLLOW SOON', 'The Sou’wester is a quiet, gated apartment community located in the “Top Hat” area of Seattle.', 'These spacious apartment homes are just steps from Metro bus routes 128, and 137, giving you quick easy access to downtown.', 'You will also enjoy the ease of walking to local shopping and activities.', 'All of these well designed floor plans feature either a large balcony or a garden-friendly yard.', 'If you need closet space look no further, large closets in bedrooms and entry area.', 'All apartment homes are cable & high speed internet ready.', 'When summer comes you can enjoy the in-ground pool area!', 'We also provide laundry facilities on site and assigned parking for residents.', 'Please call us at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a tour.', 'RENTAL UNIT AMENITIES', 'Refrigerator', 'Balcony', 'BUILDING AMENITIES', 'On-site Laundry', 'Swimming Pool', 'OTHER PRICING DETAILS', 'Available Date:\xa0\xa0\xa0Fri Aug 19, 2022', 'Deposit:\xa0\xa0\xa0800.00', 'Minimum Lease:\xa0\xa0\xa012', 'Utilities:\xa0\xa0\xa080', 'Non Refundable Admin Fee:\xa0\xa0\xa0150', 'CONTACT INFO', 'Leasing Office', 'show contact info']
